{
  "video_id": "Kxg0_EpOcWs",
  "title": "The Chinese zodiac, explained | ShaoLan",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12891.0,
      "end_time": 15713.0,
      "text": "Have you ever been asked by your Chinese friend,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15713.0,
      "end_time": 17947.0,
      "text": "&quot;What is your zodiac sign?&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17947.0,
      "end_time": 20456.0,
      "text": "Don&#39;t think they are making small talk."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 20456.0,
      "end_time": 22407.0,
      "text": "If you say, &quot;I&#39;m a Monkey,&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 22407.0,
      "end_time": 23790.0,
      "text": "they immediately know"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 23790.0,
      "end_time": 27210.0,
      "text": "you are either 24, 36, 48 or 60 years old."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 27210.0,
      "end_time": 28240.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 28240.0,
      "end_time": 32616.0,
      "text": "Asking a zodiac sign is a polite way of asking your age."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 32616.0,
      "end_time": 36529.0,
      "text": "By revealing your zodiac sign, you are also being evaluated."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 36529.0,
      "end_time": 40593.0,
      "text": "Judgments are being made about your fortune or misfortune,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 40593.0,
      "end_time": 42995.0,
      "text": "your personality, career prospects"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 42995.0,
      "end_time": 45322.0,
      "text": "and how you will do in a given year."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 45322.0,
      "end_time": 48242.0,
      "text": "If you share you and your partner&#39;s animal signs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 48242.0,
      "end_time": 52725.0,
      "text": "they will paint a picture in their mind about your private life."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 52725.0,
      "end_time": 55372.0,
      "text": "Maybe you don&#39;t believe in the Chinese zodiac."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 55372.0,
      "end_time": 59227.0,
      "text": "As a quarter of the world population is influenced by it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 59227.0,
      "end_time": 62406.0,
      "text": "you&#39;d be wise to do something about that."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 62406.0,
      "end_time": 65991.0,
      "text": "So what is the Chinese zodiac, exactly?"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 65991.0,
      "end_time": 69211.0,
      "text": "Most Westerners think of Greco-Roman zodiac,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 69211.0,
      "end_time": 71973.0,
      "text": "the signs divided into 12 months."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 71973.0,
      "end_time": 73948.0,
      "text": "The Chinese zodiac is different."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 73948.0,
      "end_time": 77150.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a 12-year cycle labeled with animals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 77150.0,
      "end_time": 79750.0,
      "text": "starting with a Rat and ending with a Pig,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 79750.0,
      "end_time": 83663.0,
      "text": "and has no association with constellations."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 83663.0,
      "end_time": 89273.0,
      "text": "For example, if you were born in 1975, you are a Rabbit."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 89273.0,
      "end_time": 92139.0,
      "text": "Can you see your zodiac sign there?"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 92139.0,
      "end_time": 97448.0,
      "text": "Our Chinese ancestors constructed a very complicated theoretical framework"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 97448.0,
      "end_time": 102486.0,
      "text": "based on yin and yang, the five elements and the 12 zodiac animals."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 102486.0,
      "end_time": 104305.0,
      "text": "Over thousands of years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 104305.0,
      "end_time": 108801.0,
      "text": "this popular culture has affected people&#39;s major decisions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 108801.0,
      "end_time": 114409.0,
      "text": "such as naming, marriage, giving birth and attitude towards each other."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 114409.0,
      "end_time": 118248.0,
      "text": "And some of the implications are quite amazing."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 118248.0,
      "end_time": 123147.0,
      "text": "The Chinese believe certain animals get on better than the others."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 123147.0,
      "end_time": 127865.0,
      "text": "So parents choose specific years to give birth to babies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 127865.0,
      "end_time": 132811.0,
      "text": "because they believe the team effort by the right combination of animals"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 132811.0,
      "end_time": 135667.0,
      "text": "can give prosperity to families."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 135667.0,
      "end_time": 140630.0,
      "text": "We even refer to the zodiac when entering into romantic relations."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 140630.0,
      "end_time": 147425.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m a Pig; I should have perfect romance with Tigers, Goats and Rabbits."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 147425.0,
      "end_time": 151536.0,
      "text": "Chinese people believe some animals are natural enemies."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 151536.0,
      "end_time": 155102.0,
      "text": "As a Pig, I need to be careful with a Snake."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 155102.0,
      "end_time": 157726.0,
      "text": "Raise your hand if you are a Snake."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 157726.0,
      "end_time": 159283.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s have a chat later."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 159283.0,
      "end_time": 160702.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 160702.0,
      "end_time": 163969.0,
      "text": "We believe some animals are luckier than the others,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 163969.0,
      "end_time": 165688.0,
      "text": "such as the Dragon."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 165688.0,
      "end_time": 167570.0,
      "text": "Unlike the Western tradition,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 167570.0,
      "end_time": 172178.0,
      "text": "the Chinese Dragon is a symbol for power, strength and wealth."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 172178.0,
      "end_time": 175359.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s everyone&#39;s dream to have a Dragon baby."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 175359.0,
      "end_time": 178499.0,
      "text": "Jack Ma&#39;s parents must have been very proud."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 178499.0,
      "end_time": 180085.0,
      "text": "And they are not the only ones."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 180085.0,
      "end_time": 183006.0,
      "text": "In 2012, the Year of the Dragon,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 183006.0,
      "end_time": 185329.0,
      "text": "the birthrate in China, Hong Kong and Taiwan"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 185329.0,
      "end_time": 187596.0,
      "text": "increased by five percent."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 187596.0,
      "end_time": 192497.0,
      "text": "That means another one million more babies."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 192497.0,
      "end_time": 195434.0,
      "text": "With a traditional preference to baby boys,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 195434.0,
      "end_time": 200431.0,
      "text": "the boy-girl ratio that year was 120 to 100."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 200431.0,
      "end_time": 202219.0,
      "text": "When those Dragon boys grow up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 202219.0,
      "end_time": 207669.0,
      "text": "they will face much more severe competition in love and job markets."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 207669.0,
      "end_time": 211607.0,
      "text": "According to the BBC and the Chinese government&#39;s press release,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 211607.0,
      "end_time": 216835.0,
      "text": "January 2015 saw a peak of Cesarean sections."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 216835.0,
      "end_time": 218726.0,
      "text": "Why?"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 218726.0,
      "end_time": 222161.0,
      "text": "That was the last month for the Year of the Horse."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 222161.0,
      "end_time": 224787.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not because they like horses so much,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 224787.0,
      "end_time": 228280.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s because they try to avoid having unlucky Goat babies."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 228280.0,
      "end_time": 229382.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 229382.0,
      "end_time": 232185.0,
      "text": "If you are a Goat, please don&#39;t feel bad."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 232185.0,
      "end_time": 233939.0,
      "text": "Those are Goat babies."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 233939.0,
      "end_time": 236073.0,
      "text": "They don&#39;t look like losers to me."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 236073.0,
      "end_time": 237262.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 237262.0,
      "end_time": 240048.0,
      "text": "Tiger is another undesirable animal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 240048.0,
      "end_time": 242337.0,
      "text": "due to its volatile temperament."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 242337.0,
      "end_time": 246214.0,
      "text": "Many Chinese regions saw a sharp decline of birthrate"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 246214.0,
      "end_time": 248122.0,
      "text": "during those years."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 248122.0,
      "end_time": 251816.0,
      "text": "Perhaps one should consider zodiac in reverse,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 251816.0,
      "end_time": 256044.0,
      "text": "as those Tiger and Goat babies will face much less competition."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 256043.99999999997,
      "end_time": 260054.99999999997,
      "text": "Maybe they are the lucky ones."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 260055.0,
      "end_time": 264539.0,
      "text": "I went through the Forbes top 300 richest people in the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 264539.0,
      "end_time": 266596.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s interesting to see"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 266596.0,
      "end_time": 270198.0,
      "text": "the most undesirable two animals, the Goat and Tiger,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 270198.0,
      "end_time": 272544.0,
      "text": "are at the top of the chart,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 272544.0,
      "end_time": 274351.0,
      "text": "even higher than the Dragon."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 274351.0,
      "end_time": 276495.0,
      "text": "So maybe we should consider,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 276495.0,
      "end_time": 280384.0,
      "text": "maybe it&#39;s much better to have less competition."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 280384.0,
      "end_time": 282429.0,
      "text": "One last but interesting point:"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 282429.0,
      "end_time": 285286.0,
      "text": "many Chinese people make their investment decisions"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 285286.0,
      "end_time": 288611.0,
      "text": "based on the zodiac sign index."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 288611.0,
      "end_time": 292300.0,
      "text": "Although the belief and tradition of the zodiac sign"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 292300.0,
      "end_time": 295051.0,
      "text": "has been over thousands of years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 295051.0,
      "end_time": 298369.0,
      "text": "the trend of using it in making major decisions"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 298369.0,
      "end_time": 301934.0,
      "text": "did not really happen until the past few decades."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 301934.0,
      "end_time": 306354.0,
      "text": "Our ancestors were very busy surviving poverty, drought,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 306354.0,
      "end_time": 310028.0,
      "text": "famine, riot, disease and civil war."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 310028.0,
      "end_time": 315814.0,
      "text": "And finally, Chinese people have the time, wealth and technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 315814.0,
      "end_time": 319604.0,
      "text": "to create an ideal life they&#39;ve always wanted."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 319604.0,
      "end_time": 323275.0,
      "text": "The collective decision made by 1.3 billion people"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 323275.0,
      "end_time": 327850.0,
      "text": "has caused the fluctuation in economics and demand on everything,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 327850.0,
      "end_time": 333092.0,
      "text": "from health care and education to property and consumer goods."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 333092.0,
      "end_time": 338090.0,
      "text": "As China plays such an important role in the global economy and geopolitics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 338090.0,
      "end_time": 342223.0,
      "text": "the decisions made based on the zodiac and other Chinese traditions"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 342223.0,
      "end_time": 347203.0,
      "text": "end up impacting everyone around the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 347203.0,
      "end_time": 350030.0,
      "text": "Are there any Monkeys here?"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 350030.0,
      "end_time": 353220.0,
      "text": "2016 is the Year of the Monkey."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 353220.0,
      "end_time": 358953.0,
      "text": "Monkeys are clever, curious, creative and mischievous."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 358953.0,
      "end_time": 360135.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 360135.0,
      "end_time": 370135.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}